  "detailed_description": "<h1>💚💚 MORE UPCOMING GAMES! 💚💚</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925310/extras/bc7f6cd22ff892eb657e4efc6fbbac28.poster.avif?t=1767605128\" width=780 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925310/extras/bc7f6cd22ff892eb657e4efc6fbbac28.webm?t=1767605128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925310/extras/bc7f6cd22ff892eb657e4efc6fbbac28.mp4?t=1767605128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>🎮 4 pages comic and jigsaw Puzzle<br></li><li>😻 204 cats<br></li><li>📷 Photo mode<br></li><li>🔆 Brightness setting<br></li><li>🎨 Choose your favorite color<br></li><li>🎵 4 Musics<br></li><li>🔔 Free hints<br></li><li>💾 Save system<br></li><li>🔍 Zoom<br></li><li>🔉 Cute cat sounds<br></li><li>🎮 Gamepad compatible</li></ul><br><table><tr><th><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925310/extras/9bb63dae48437d8fbd64044f95db9261.poster.avif?t=1767605128\" width=616 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925310/extras/9bb63dae48437d8fbd64044f95db9261.webm?t=1767605128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925310/extras/9bb63dae48437d8fbd64044f95db9261.mp4?t=1767605128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Hi, welcome our experimental hidden cat project. Cats Around Us is a series that introduces wholesome silent comics as a new medium for gameplay.<br><br><strong>\"Giant Cat\"</strong> unfolds across four pages of silent comic panels by Kathrinna Rakhmavika, offering a heartwarming tale about a giant cat causing chaos in a village. A young witch must step in to resolve the situation. Throughout each page, we've hidden numerous cats for you to find while enjoying the story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925310/extras/141431f3e69a5e580e8fecda063bbf09.poster.avif?t=1767605128\" width=462 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925310/extras/141431f3e69a5e580e8fecda063bbf09.webm?t=1767605128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925310/extras/141431f3e69a5e580e8fecda063bbf09.mp4?t=1767605128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Additionally, we've included a photo mode for players to capture intriguing moments from the comic, allowing them to colorize and share their creations with the world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925310/extras/fb795fdc2d5584763df3a1a20df61c35.poster.avif?t=1767605128\" width=462 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925310/extras/fb795fdc2d5584763df3a1a20df61c35.webm?t=1767605128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925310/extras/fb795fdc2d5584763df3a1a20df61c35.mp4?t=1767605128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925310/extras/c81fa7167fdb3615313064fa52cf47ac.poster.avif?t=1767605128\" width=616 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925310/extras/c81fa7167fdb3615313064fa52cf47ac.webm?t=1767605128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925310/extras/c81fa7167fdb3615313064fa52cf47ac.mp4?t=1767605128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></th></tr></table>",
